{"tid":261384,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"同fd zone 咗好耐嘅fd拍拖前要諗清楚","createTime":"2017-05-28T12:10:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-29T06:29:55.000Z","uid":2068,"like":6,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6c49e6171c036ad4914f13605813c494b5f3a4ca","tid":261384,"uid":2068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T12:10:04.000Z","msg":"就算佢同你講一齊係講緣份 講timing 講搵到一個就夠 <br />\n屌收皮啦 <br />\n識咗幾多年都好 一分手就變唔返之前咁fd 咩都講咩都玩 就算單獨出街，攬頭攬頸都唔會覺得有咩問題 <br />\n<br />\n試過同個識咗8年嘅fd拍拖一個月散 仲要帽我<br />\n隔兩年同識咗3年 日對夜對嘅fd拍，又係拍左一個月就散 之後仲要對多年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實真係好後悔，點解一開始嘅時候無諗清楚<br />\n一時衝動就一齊咗<br />\n如果真係愛你嘅唔會fd zone咗咁耐先溝啦"},{"pid":"73e80062c4b9cf5fee3289bc445b5cf2c8431dca","tid":261384,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T12:12:21.000Z","msg":"啱聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"685373e8c96e1e9cb6573949d274e6c91baad365","tid":261384,"uid":116609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T12:15:50.000Z","msg":"藍絲？"},{"pid":"9b74ce9014f8493e38495a97b1d9d9113978a059","tid":261384,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T12:18:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>藍絲？</blockquote><br />\n應該係"},{"pid":"fa0b12673472d1f6186a9afa4b0dfd6366de914d","tid":261384,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T12:19:05.000Z","msg":"佢地突然向你表白？"},{"pid":"19e18c6b995e7f5fbd41c78ba35289252f29200b","tid":261384,"uid":2068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T12:19:14.000Z","msg":"雖然一個月感情都唔深 不值一提<br />\n就係短短嘅時間 無咗咁多年朋友 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好後悔"},{"pid":"813c461baf52d589c856895651ac6fc016d95f1b","tid":261384,"uid":56935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T12:20:02.000Z","msg":"樓主男定女？"},{"pid":"bf5177a80b143bd422c13a6ee62c4834c263d0be","tid":261384